                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I think that's how it works: Mob damage while charmed is 50% of the base damage + 33% of the damage interval. A mob with base damage of 109 and max hit of 508 will hit for a min of 54 and a max of roughly 225 (0.33*(508-109)+54). Mob hitting for 685 with base hit of 110 will hit for 245 (0.33(685-110)+55).
<br />

<br />
Or something to that effect.
<br />

<br />
It blows either way.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
