                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">SUGGESTIONS?</span>
<br />

<br />
First I think we need some parses. How much DPS are these mobs that hit for 220-245? Are they about the same as a BoT DC pet, then? More? I'm starting to lean towards the idea that they should just do an across-the-board upgrade to our animations to give them more HP and allow THEM to hit for 200. A 65% DPS-nerfed pet has a risk:reward ratio of  2.857. That's ridiculous.
<br />

<br />
Bottom line: if we are going to be LESS effective at DPS we ought to suffer LESS risk, not more.
<br />

<br />
Second, I think they ought to take the whole thing back and apologize to us. But that's just me.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=361216" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ariu <span style="font-style: italic">stop destroying my class damnit!</span> Vil''''Aki &lt;Heroes&gt;</a>
<br />
